title: Paul McCartney delivers private show to Philly trucking gala
text: > Entertainment Paul McCartney delivers private show to Philly trucking gala FILE - In this June 19, 2015 file photo, Paul McCartney performs on Day 2 of the 2015 Firefly Music Festival at The Woodlands in Dover, Del. McCartney gave a private performance in Philadelphia last Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015 during the American Trucking Association’s Management Conference and Exhibition. McCartney changed the lyrics to the Beatles song “Drive My Car” to play to the crowd of about 1,000. (Photo by Owen Sweeney/Invision/AP)
